---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About WD Land - Expert Land Development Team"
  description="Learn about WD Land's experienced team, our commitment to sustainable development, and our proven track record of transforming raw land into thriving communities."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-16 lg:pt-20">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-secondary-50">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center fade-in-scroll">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-6">
            About WD Land
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-secondary-600 leading-relaxed">
            For over two decades, we've been transforming raw land into valuable, sustainable communities through expert planning, innovative design, and responsible development practices.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Story -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="fade-in-scroll">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-6">
              Our Story
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-secondary-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              WD Land was founded on the belief that every piece of land has untapped potential waiting to be discovered. What started as a small team of passionate developers has grown into a comprehensive land development company with a reputation for excellence and integrity.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Our journey began with a simple mission: to transform raw land into thriving communities while preserving the natural beauty and environmental integrity of each site. Over the years, we've refined our approach, incorporating the latest sustainable development practices and cutting-edge technology to deliver exceptional results.
            </p>
            <p class="text-secondary-600 leading-relaxed">
              Today, WD Land stands as a trusted partner for property owners, investors, and communities seeking professional land development services. Our portfolio spans residential, commercial, and mixed-use developments, each designed to enhance property values while contributing positively to the surrounding area.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="fade-in-scroll">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-accent-100 rounded-2xl p-8 h-96 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 mx-auto">
                  <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Innovation & Excellence</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary-600">
                  Combining traditional expertise with modern innovation to deliver exceptional results.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Our Values -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-secondary-50">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-6">
            Our Core Values
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-secondary-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            These principles guide every decision we make and every project we undertake.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="stagger-container grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="stagger-item card p-8 text-center opacity-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Integrity</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              We conduct business with honesty, transparency, and ethical practices in all our relationships and transactions.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="stagger-item card p-8 text-center opacity-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Sustainability</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              Environmental stewardship is at the heart of our development process, ensuring projects benefit both people and planet.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="stagger-item card p-8 text-center opacity-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Excellence</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              We strive for the highest standards in every aspect of our work, from initial planning to final completion.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="stagger-item card p-8 text-center opacity-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Collaboration</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              We work closely with clients, communities, and stakeholders to ensure every project meets diverse needs and expectations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="stagger-item card p-8 text-center opacity-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Innovation</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              We embrace new technologies and methodologies to improve efficiency, reduce costs, and enhance project outcomes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="stagger-item card p-8 text-center opacity-0">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-4">Value Creation</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              Our focus is on maximizing long-term value for our clients while creating positive impacts for communities.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Team Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-white">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in-scroll">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-6">
            Our Expert Team
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-secondary-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            Our multidisciplinary team brings together decades of experience in land development, engineering, environmental science, and project management.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center fade-in-scroll">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-primary-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-2">Development Specialists</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              Expert planners and developers with extensive experience in residential, commercial, and mixed-use projects.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center fade-in-scroll">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-100 to-green-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-2">Environmental Consultants</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              Environmental scientists and consultants ensuring sustainable development practices and regulatory compliance.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center fade-in-scroll">
            <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-100 to-accent-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-accent-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-secondary-900 mb-2">Project Managers</h3>
            <p class="text-secondary-600">
              Experienced project managers ensuring on-time, on-budget delivery with exceptional quality standards.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 to-primary-800">
      <div class="container-custom text-center fade-in-scroll">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6">
          Ready to Work with WD Land?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Experience the difference that expertise, integrity, and innovation make in land development. Contact us today to discuss your project.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary btn-hover bg-white text-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-50">
            Get Started Today
          </a>
          <a href="/services" class="btn-primary btn-hover bg-primary-500 hover:bg-primary-400 border-primary-400">
            View Our Services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>